<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Zoogastric disinterest -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Dislikes.label>不喜为兽食</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Dislikes.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn dislikes being prey for animals. How certain can it be that the beast will listen to demands to be let out? -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Dislikes.description>这个角色不喜欢被动物吞食。它怎么能确定那头野兽会听从"放我出去"的要求呢？</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Dislikes.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Zoogastric interest -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Likes.label>愿为兽食</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Likes.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn likes being prey for animals. It's thrilling to be subject to the inscrutable whims of a beast, not knowing if it might change its mind about its safety, or when it'll decide to release it. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Likes.description>这个角色喜欢被动物吞食。置身于野兽那难以捉摸的任性之中，不知道它会不会改变主意，不知道它何时才肯松口——这种未知的感觉令人兴奋。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Likes.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Zoogastric ambivalence -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Neutral.label>为兽食随缘</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Neutral.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn doesn't mind being prey for animals, but doesn't prefer it either. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Neutral.description>这个角色不排斥被动物吞食，但也没有特别的偏好。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Neutral.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Zoogastric obsession -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Obsessed.label>痴迷为兽食</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Obsessed.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn adores being prey for animals. If it ever goes missing, make sure to check the bellies of all your livestock, pets, and the wildlife. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Obsessed.description>这个角色对成为动物的盘中餐痴迷不已。如果哪天它失踪了，记得去检查一下所有牲畜、宠物和野生动物的肚子。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Obsessed.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Zoogastric revulsion -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Refuses.label>拒为兽食</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Refuses.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn hates being prey for animals and will never willingly be consumed by them. It's as disgusting as it is degrading. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Refuses.description>这个角色厌恶被动物吞食，绝不会主动让它们吃掉自己。这事既恶心又掉价。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Animals_Refuses.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Anthropogastric disinterest -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Dislikes.label>不喜为食于人</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Dislikes.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn dislikes being prey for its fellow sapient beings. It can't escape the stresses of society by entering the body of a member of society. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Dislikes.description>这个角色不喜欢被其他智慧生物吞食。钻进另一个社会成员的肚子里，可没法让它逃离社会的压力。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Dislikes.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Anthropogastric interest -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Likes.label>愿为食于人</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Likes.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn likes being prey for its fellow sapient beings. It's nice to be able to socialize with its predator. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Likes.description>这个角色喜欢被其他智慧生物吞食。能和自己的捕食者交流互动，感觉还不错。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Likes.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Anthropogastric ambivalence -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Neutral.label>为食于人随缘</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Neutral.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn doesn't mind being prey for its fellow sapient beings, but doesn't prefer it either. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Neutral.description>这个角色不排斥被其他智慧生物吞食，但也没有特别的偏好。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Neutral.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Anthropogastric obsession -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Obsessed.label>痴迷为食于人</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Obsessed.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn adores being prey for its fellow sapient beings. It is a prey of the people- -any person, really. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Obsessed.description>这个角色对成为其他智慧生物的食物痴迷不已。它属于人民——属于任何人的食物，真的。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Obsessed.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Anthropogastric revulsion -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Refuses.label>拒为食于人</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Refuses.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn hates being prey for its fellow sapient beings and will never willingly be consumed by them. That's at least three kinds of unnatural. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Refuses.description>这个角色厌恶被其他智慧生物吞食，绝不会主动让他们吃掉自己。这至少违背了三种自然法则。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Humanoids_Refuses.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Entomogastric disinterest -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Dislikes.label>不喜为虫食</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Dislikes.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn dislikes being prey for insectoids. Bugs aren't known for eating their prey in one whole bite. Not swarms of them, at least... -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Dislikes.description>这个角色不喜欢被虫族吞食。虫子们可从来不会一口把猎物整个吞下去——至少成群结队的时候不会……</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Dislikes.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Entomogastric interest -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Likes.label>愿为虫食</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Likes.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn likes being prey for insectoids. Such an alien physiology is quite fascinating to tour from the inside. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Likes.description>这个角色喜欢被虫族吞食。从内部游览一番那种异星生理构造，着实令人着迷。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Likes.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Entomogastric ambivalence -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Neutral.label>为虫食随缘</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Neutral.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn doesn't mind being prey for insectoids, but doesn't prefer it either. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Neutral.description>这个角色不排斥被虫族吞食，但也没有特别的偏好。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Neutral.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Entomogastric obsession -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Obsessed.label>痴迷为虫食</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Obsessed.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn adores being prey for insectoids. There aren't many other ways for a humanoid to become one with the hive. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Obsessed.description>这个角色对成为虫族的食物痴迷不已。对于一个类人生物来说，要成为虫巢的一部分，除了这条路也没多少别的选择了。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Obsessed.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Entomogastric revulsion -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Refuses.label>拒为虫食</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Refuses.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn hates being prey for insectoids and will not willingly be consumed by them. No amount of showers would ever let it feel clean again. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Refuses.description>这个角色厌恶被虫族吞食，绝不会主动让它们吃掉自己。洗多少次澡都洗不掉那种脏兮兮的感觉。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Insectoids_Refuses.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Mechanogastric disinterest -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Dislikes.label>不喜为械食</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Dislikes.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn dislikes being prey for mechanoids. Think of all the grinding gears! All the constant clicking and ticking! -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Dislikes.description>这个角色不喜欢被机械体吞食。想想那些嘎吱作响的齿轮！还有那无休止的咔嗒声和滴答声！</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Dislikes.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Mechanogastric interest -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Likes.label>愿为械食</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Likes.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn likes being prey for mechanoids. Cold, unyielding plasteel makes for a unique and exhilarating experience. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Likes.description>这个角色喜欢被机械体吞食。冰冷而坚硬的塑钢内壁，带来一种独特而令人振奋的体验。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Likes.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Mechanogastric ambivalence -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Neutral.label>为械食随缘</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Neutral.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn doesn't mind being prey for mechanoids, but doesn't prefer it either. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Neutral.description>这个角色不排斥被机械体吞食，但也没有特别的偏好。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Neutral.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Mechanogastric obsession -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Obsessed.label>痴迷为械食</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Obsessed.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn adores being prey for mechanoids. It is more at home among flexing hydraulics and humming circuits than the beat of most hearts. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Obsessed.description>这个角色对成为机械体的食物痴迷不已。比起大多数心脏的跳动声，它在液压杆的伸缩和电路的嗡鸣中反而更自在。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Obsessed.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Mechanogastric revulsion -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Refuses.label>拒为械食</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Refuses.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn hates being prey for mechanoids and will not willingly be consumed by them. Even if it was suicidal, that sure as hell ain't the way it wants to go out. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Refuses.description>这个角色厌恶被机械体吞食，绝不会主动让它们吃掉自己。就算它想寻死，也绝对不想以这种方式了结。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Prey_Mechanoids_Refuses.description>
  
</LanguageData>